node.text:
Peaceful & Pretty in Pink ☺️💖

We’ve all experienced some form of anxiety and stress. When our goals aren’t coming together as we planned them. When our relationships seem too complicated. When an important decision must be made, but we don’t know which path to take. These scenarios and more may cause our minds to be troubled, frustrated, and overall anxious.

Anxiety stems from fear of the future. From thinking too much about “what if”. The threat of the unknown… While some amount of anxiety is normal, does it really make sense to be anxious about things that haven’t even happened yet?

What if things work out even better than you dreamed? We can’t allow negative thoughts of worry to destroy our peace, our joy, our lives. 

Learning how to relax and let things flow is easier said than done. Focus on what you can do and have faith that those other battles have already been won. 

#Peace #PrettyInPink #Anxiety #Fear #Frustration #Relax #Love #LetThingsFlow #Peaceful #Happy
#TheBattlesHaveAlreadyBeenWon

node.text:
☀️ >📱
According to research, the average person spends over 76,500 hours of their life looking at their cellphone screen. That’s about 8.74 years... 

When life is already so short, my hope is for us to truly live. Focus on making every second count!

#ImStillHere #FocusedOnPriorities #LifeIsShort #EyesUpNotDown #Live #Love #Learn #Grow #Create #FindPeace #FindJoy #MakeLifeBeautiful #MentalHealthAdvice #SpendLessTimeLookingAtThePhone #SpendMoreTimeDoingThingsWeLove

node.text:
The Fact Is (I need you) - Jill Scott

I could be congresswoman 
Or a garbage woman
A police officer or a carpenter
I could be a doctor and a lawyer
And a mother and a "Good God woman what u done to me?" 
Kind of lover I can be
I could be a computer analyst
The queen with the nappy hair raising her fist
Or I could be much more and a myraid of this
Hot as the summer
Sweet as the first kiss
And even though I can do all these things
I need you
We need you

#King #Queen #YouAreNeeded #Natural #WinterNights #StayHome

node.text:
I am so in love with these drawings by @anya_zalesskaya! My personal road to becoming a Neuropsychiatrist has been filled with so many highs and lows. I’ve taken 7 steps forward 8 steps back. I’ve succeeded in the most difficult times and failed in others. However, one thing about me is that no matter what, I don’t give up! Thank you all for your continued support during this journey. Your comments, messages, and drawings like these truly mean so much to me! ❤️ I can’t wait to heal and serve.👩🏾‍⚕️🩺 

#DoctorJoi #Neuropsychiatry #MentalHealth #MedicalSchool #Residency #BlackDoctors #MelaninInMedicine #RoadToSuccess #LearnFromYourFailures #TrueSuccessStories #WorkHard #NeverGiveUp

Educated Introvert 😌

Signs That You May Be An Introvert:
1. Crowds of people drain your energy 
2. You enjoy having “quiet time”
3. You have a small group of friends 
4. Others may find it hard to get to know you 
5. High self-awareness/ understanding 
6. You learn by observation 
7. You prefer independence 

#Introverted #Energy #Quiet #SelfAwareness #RealFriends #Observer #Independent #LoveYourselfAndYourGifts
